Class TypeParameter<T>

java.lang.Object
com.google.common.reflect.TypeParameter<T>
public abstract class TypeParameter<T> extends Object
Captures a free type variable that can be used in TypeToken.where(TypeParameter, TypeToken). For example: 
static <T> TypeToken<List<T>> listOf(Class<T> elementType) {
  return new TypeToken<List<T>>() {}
      .where(new TypeParameter<T>() {}, elementType);
}
Since:
12.0
Author:
Ben Yu
